author: Just Jared
title: Bella & Gigi Hadid Join Protestors in New York City
text:
Bella and Gigi Hadid are surrounded by protestors during an immigration ban march on Sunday (January 29) in New York City.
The model sisters were joined by a couple of friends as they held up signs that read “Resist” and “We are all humans.”
PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Gigi Hadid 
Earlier in the day, Gigi and Bella headed out of their hotel with their mom Yolanda . Perhaps on their way to the protest?
The week before, Gigi tweeted out her support for the Women’s March.
Also pictured: Bella keeping covered up while out and about on Saturday (January 28) in New York City.
10+ pictures inside of the Hadid sisters out in New York…
